description.desc: With great reflexes, enables one to avoid the monster's attack.
description.name: Shadow Shifter

description.desc: Stab a monster with a dagger that's been smeared with poison; the monster struck has a chance of being poisoned.  Usable up to 3 times against each monster.
description.name: Venomous Stab

description.desc: Increase all players' stats within a party by certain percentage
description.name: Maple Warrior

description.desc: Strikes an unsuspecting monster at its vital spots 4 times. The last strike can be lethal with a given success rate.  Only works with Dark Sight enabled.
description.name: Assassinate

description.desc: Provokes a monster, causing its general defense to increase. As a result, EXP earned and drop rate for items will increase for this monster.
description.name: Taunt

description.desc: For a set period of time, a group of ninjas hiding around the bushes will periodically ambush up to 6 monsters at once. : #cShadow Shifter level 5 and above#
description.name: Ninja Ambush

description.desc: Sets off a smoke grenade to escape from a tight situation. All members of the party in the vicinity of smoke will not receive damage while the smokescreen is up.
description.name: Smokescreen

description.desc: With great quickness, stabs multiple monsters TWICE. Under the set success rate, the monsters attacked will be stunned.
description.name: Boomerang Step
